      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Harlequin Apex Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Austere Maid",
        "Description": "Good evening, Master Hunter.\r\nI hate to disturb you in this late\r\nhour, but I have received word\r\nthat an Apex Mizutsune was\r\nspotted along my employer\u0027s\r\nroute home. I ask that you\r\nguarantee his safe return.",
        "Target": "Hunt an Apex Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Mizutsune sup\u00E9rieur arlequin",
        "Client": "Servante aust\u00E8re",
        "Description": "D\u00E9sol\u00E9e de te d\u00E9ranger \u00E0 une heure\r\nsi tardive, mais j\u0027ai appris qu\u0027un\r\nMizutsune sup\u00E9rieur a \u00E9t\u00E9 aper\u00E7u\r\nsur le trajet de mon employeur.\r\nEst-ce que tu pourrais le\r\nprot\u00E9ger, s\u0027il te pla\u00EEt ?",
        "Target": "Chasser un Mizutsune sup\u00E9rieur",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il Mizutsune Apex variopinto",
        "Client": "Damigella austera",
        "Description": "Buonasera, detesto disturbarti\r\na quest\u0027ora tarda, ma ho\r\nsaputo che un Mizutsune Apex \u00E8\r\nstato avvistato sulla via di\r\nritorno del mio capo.\r\nTi prego, assicurati che\r\ntorni a casa incolume.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Mizutsune Apex",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der ulkige Apex-Mizutsune",
        "Client": "Ernstes Hausm\u00E4dchen",
        "Description": "Guten Abend w\u00FCnsche ich. Ich\r\nst\u00F6re nur ungern so sp\u00E4t, aber\r\nich habe erfahren, dass ein\r\nApex-Mizutsune auf dem Heim-\r\nweg meines Arbeitgebers ge-\r\nsichtet wurde. Ich bitte Euch,\r\nf\u00FCr seine Sicherheit zu b\u00FCrgen.",
